seo: Oracle EBS,文件读取漏洞,bispgrapgh,jsp,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测Oracle E-Business Suite中的bispgrapgh.jsp文件读取漏洞，通过构造特定的URL请求来验证是否存在漏洞并返回相关信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the file read vulnerability in bispgrapgh.jsp of Oracle E-Business Suite. It constructs specific URL requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability and returns relevant information.
